External datasets used
----------------------

The Revolution Crossroads Hugging Face datasets (Smithsonian / LOC /
NARA) used by this prototype are CC0-1.0 (public domain). See
`data/scratch/hackathon-smithsonian/dataset-quality-reference.md` for
verified row counts, sizes, and license citations per dataset.

The `apexlon` codebase (separate repository, not part of this fork) is
referenced in adr.md and repo-bridge.md as a *pattern source* only —
no code from apexlon is incorporated into this repository at runtime.
The 5-dimension OECD KPI rubric and append-only ledger pattern in
`code/governance/` are independently authored implementations of the
same conceptual approach, designed to operate without an apexlon
dependency.

